    "en": {
      "name": "Lunalight Silver Hound",
      "effect": "If this card is sent to the GY by card effect: You can Special Summon 1 \"Lunalight\" monster from your Deck, except \"Lunalight Silver Hound\", and if you do, you cannot Special Summon from the Extra Deck, except \"Lunalight\" monsters, while you control that face-up monster. When a Spell/Trap Card or effect is activated on the field (Quick Effect): You can banish from your GY, this card and 1 \"Lunalight\" Fusion Monster; negate the activation. You can only use each effect of \"Lunalight Silver Hound\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
